Package org.cpsolver.instructor.model Description

Instructor Scheduling: Model. Instructor Scheduling problem model. The model is implemented by InstructorSchedulingModel. Variables are TeachingRequest, values are TeachingAssignment. Each teaching request has a course (see Course) and one or more sections (see {link Section}). Each assignment assigns one instructor (see Instructor) to a single teaching request.
Version:
IFS 1.3 (Instructor Sectioning)
